编译安装Python时系统缺少zlib组件导致setuptools无法安装
安装好zlib后重新编译Python即可


select user();   ---查看mysql当前用户
select host,user,password from mysql.user;
mysqladmin -u root -p password 123456 --更改root密码为123456，后续需输入原密码
set password for 'peng'@'localhost'=PASSWORD('XSXXXXXXXXX');

show grants for peng;
grant all privileges on python3.* to peng@localhost identified by '1234';
flush privileges;

MySQL密码重置
mysqld_safe --skip-grant-tables &
然后以无密码模式登录root修改密码
update mysql.user set password=PASSWORD('XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX') where user='XXXXX';

